title: i want to live in a skyrim house
author: Gus Johnson
description:
i like skyrim
↓FOLLOW ME HERE OR I WILL CRY (HARD)↓
- ADD THE SONG ON SPOTIFY: https://spoti.fi/2NqTFjN
- Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/gusjohnson​​

- SUBSCRIBE TO THE PODCAST: https://bit.ly/2wA7zDR​​
- Instagram: instagram.com/johnsongus
- Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/gustoonz​​
- Reddit: https://www.reddit.com/r/gusjohnson/​​
- Snapchat: motherxteresa

thank you for listening to my skyrim song. you can listen to it everywhere i think. 

Gus Johnson plays all sorts of characters, from Mitchell Robbins to JK Rowling to some guy in God's Country to Imbiamba Jombes to filming videos with his mom to pillow guy to the my pool guy to the Gus & Eddy Podcast to small town reviews to shotguns in movies to the tough kid growing up to your friend who has a knife to spotify ad guy to... I don't know why I am writing this in third person. I am Gus. I wrote this. Also subscribe to the Gus & Eddy Podcast please. Eddy Burback and I make it and it's ok. My brother is Sven Johnson, that guy's alright.

Thanks for watching and sharing! Don't stab people. I'll see you later.

谢谢你听我的skyrim歌曲。 你可以听它无处不在，我想。

格斯-约翰逊扮演各种角色，从米切尔-罗宾斯到JK-罗琳，再到《上帝的国度》中的一些人，到Imbiamba Jombes，再到和他妈妈一起拍摄视频，再到枕头男，再到我的游泳池男，再到Gus & Eddy播客，再到小镇评论，再到电影中的猎枪，再到长大后的坚强孩子，再到你的朋友，他有一把刀，再到Spotify广告男...... 我不知道为什么我写这个第三人称。我是格斯。我写了这个。也请订阅Gus & Eddy播客。我和Eddy Burback一起做的，没问题的。我哥哥是Sven Johnson，那家伙还不错。

谢谢你的观看和分享！不要刺伤别人 回头见
